"title": "6186: imagination, evil scheming",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6186",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human thinking, darkened by sin, expressed in plans which are in opposition to God and which seek to take advantage of others.</p>\n<h2>Human thought is darkened by sin</h2>\n<h3>As a result of rejecting God's revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2-Ps10:4\">PSA 10:2–10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14\">2CO 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:18\">EPH 4:17–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:15\">TIT 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>As a result of excessive alcohol</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:33\">PRO 23:33</a></p>\n<h3>As a result of Satan's activity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h2>Sinful human thinking finds expression in evil ways</h2>\n<h3>In evil schemes and plans</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:16-Prov6:18\">PRO 6:16–6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:6\">GEN 11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:4\">PSA 36:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:5-Ps64:6\">PSA 64:5–64:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:14\">PRO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:20\">PRO 12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:22\">PRO 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:8-Prov24:9\">PRO 24:8–24:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:11\">ECC 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:30\">ROM 1:30</a></p>\n<h3>In scheming against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:5\">2CO 10:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:21\">DEU 31:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:2\">PSA 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:15\">HOS 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:11\">NAM 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>In scheming against others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:60-Lam3:61\">LAM 3:60–3:61</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:9\">DEU 15:9</a> <em>warnings against evil thinking as the year for cancelling debts approaches</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:27\">JOB 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2-Ps10:3\">PSA 10:2–10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:7\">PSA 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:12\">PSA 38:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:7-Ps41:8\">PSA 41:7–41:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:1-Ps140:2\">PSA 140:1–140:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:7\">ISA 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:3-Matt26:4\">MAT 26:3–26:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:1-Mark14:2\">MRK 14:1–14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:1-Luke22:2\">LUK 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:53\">JHN 11:53</a> <em>Jewish religious leaders plot against Jesus Christ.</em></p>\n<h3>Human plans are an expression of pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:16\">JAS 4:13–4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:11\">PRO 18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:7-Isa10:11\">ISA 10:7–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:20\">LUK 12:16–12:20</a></p>\n<h3>Evil plans will fail</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:51\">LUK 1:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:25\">EST 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:11-Ps21:12\">PSA 21:11–21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10\">PSA 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:10\">ISA 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:18\">ISA 66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:9\">NAM 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>False prophecy comes from evil thinking</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:2-Ezek13:3\">EZK 13:2–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:3\">DEU 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:16-Jer23:17\">JER 23:16–23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:17\">EZK 13:17</a></p>",
